        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost">Isidi Sera</supplied>pi aedem <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">simulacr</supplied>a porticus <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">Numas N</supplied>umeni <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">Alexandri</supplied>nus <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">devot</supplied>us faciu<lb break="no" n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">ndum <expan><abbr>cur</abbr><ex>avit</ex></expan></supplied> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <supplied reason="lost">Εἴσιδι Σ</supplied>αράπι <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">ναὸν χο</supplied>άνα <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">στο</supplied>ὰν Νουμᾶς <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">Νουμε</supplied>νίου Ἀλε<lb break="no" n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">ξαν</supplied>δρεὺς <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">εὐσ</supplied>εβ&amp;lt;ὴ=Ε&amp;gt;ς∙ ἐπόει 
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Iscrizione composta da due frammenti, a-b. Nel campo Fundstelle e Aufbewahrung la prima indicazione si riferisce al primo frammento, a, la seconda al secondo, b. Le misure del pezzo e delle lettere scritte sopra si riferiscono al frammento a. Fr. b: Höhe -19.7; Breite -18.4; Tiefe -6. Buchstabenhöhe fr. b: 1.8-2.3.</p>
            </div>
